name: Misfit Love
description:
'Misfit Love' print (420x297mm, 350gsm silk card, hand-numbered and signed). Your print will be dispatched asap via first class post.  

This print was created as part of the publicity material for Misfit Love, my first ever exhibition which took place in September 2013 at the SHO gallery in Cardiff. Perfect for zombie couples!

name: Hometown Cardiff
description:
'Hometown Cardiff' print (420x297mm, 350gsm silk card). Your print will be dispatched asap via first class post.  

This print featuring a host of Cardiff landmarks was created to accompany the launch of the We Are Cardiff documentary Portrait of a City.

This regular edition print is NOT signed or numbered - the initial limited edition print (without the 'Cardiff' text) sold out so this version was released due to further demand.
